[I] System log viewer tool

[T] KSystemLog show all logs of your system, grouped by General (Default system
[T] log, Authentication, Kernel, X.org...), and optional Services (Apache,
[T] Cups, etc, ...).

[U] https://apps.kde.org/ksystemlog/

